This JAR is a regular (non-shaded) library JAR. It embeds the following
resource within the JAR:

  reaper.jar — a shaded uber JAR produced by the Altcontainers Reaper
  module. The reaper module bundles and relocates its own third-party
  dependencies. See the reaper artifact's NOTICE for its third-party
  attribution.

The following compile-scope dependencies are declared in the POM and are
resolved from the consuming application's classpath at runtime (they are
NOT bundled or relocated in this JAR):

  com.github.docker-java:docker-java-core:3.4.2        (Apache 2.0)
  com.github.docker-java:docker-java-transport-zerodep:3.4.2 (Apache 2.0)
  org.slf4j:slf4j-api:2.0.18                            (MIT)

docker-java-core transitively pulls in Jackson (Apache 2.0), Commons IO
(Apache 2.0), Commons Compress (Apache 2.0), Commons Lang (Apache 2.0),
Guava (Apache 2.0), and Bouncy Castle (MIT). docker-java-transport-zerodep
is itself a shaded uber JAR bundling Apache HttpClient 5, HttpCore 5,
Commons Codec, and Bouncy Castle.
